--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 1
Use case        : variables management
Scenario name   : add variable
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Variabili" and then "Aggiungi".
4. Insert values and press the button "Conferma".

Expected results:

1. The new variable is added to the system.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 2
Use case        : variable management
Scenario name   : modify variable
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert an emailtemplate as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Modifica" in the variables list page, for the variable
   just inserted.

Expected results:

1. The variable is correctly changed.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 3
Use case        : variable management
Scenario name   : delete variable 
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert an emailtemplate as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Cancella" and confirm the deletion.

Expected results:

1. The variable is correctly deleted.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 4
Use case        : variable management
Scenario name   : paging
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert 25 variables repeating 25 times scenario 1.
5. Verify the paging adding, removing end changing the variables.

Expected results:

1. The variables paging works fine.

